SELECT "title"."imdb_index", "title"."imdb_id", max("title"."production_year") as agg_0, min("title"."episode_nr") as agg_1, min("title"."id") as agg_2 FROM "title" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"  WHERE "keyword"."id" BETWEEN 42181 AND 76264 AND "movie_keyword"."id" >= 3394034 AND CAST("keyword"."phonetic_code" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%R1%652%' AND "title"."id" BETWEEN 1048026 AND 1183807 GROUP BY "title"."imdb_index", "title"."imdb_id" ORDER BY "title"."imdb_index", "title"."imdb_id";

SELECT "info_type"."info", "info_type"."id", min("movie_info_idx"."info_type_id") as agg_0 FROM "movie_info_idx" LEFT OUTER JOIN "info_type" ON "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" = "info_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "kind_type" ON "title"."kind_id" = "kind_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"  WHERE "movie_companies"."id" <= 2324712 AND CAST("info_type"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%noise%' GROUP BY "info_type"."info", "info_type"."id" ORDER BY "info_type"."info", "info_type"."id";

SELECT "cast_info"."role_id", sum("title"."id") as agg_0, min("title"."production_year") as agg_1, max("title"."episode_of_id") as agg_2 FROM "kind_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "kind_type"."id" = "title"."kind_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2005.7856822255533 AND "title"."id" <= 1857518 AND "kind_type"."kind" != 'tv series' GROUP BY "cast_info"."role_id" ORDER BY "cast_info"."role_id";

SELECT "movie_companies"."company_type_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("company_name"."id") as agg_1 FROM "company_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id"  WHERE CAST("movie_info"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%D%utch%' GROUP BY "movie_companies"."company_type_id" ORDER BY "movie_companies"."company_type_id";

SELECT avg("movie_companies"."movie_id") as agg_0 FROM "movie_companies" LEFT OUTER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"  WHERE "company_type"."id" = 2 AND CAST("movie_companies"."note" AS varchar) LIKE '%(USA)%' AND CAST("company_type"."kind" AS varchar) LIKE '%c%ompanies%' AND ("movie_companies"."movie_id" BETWEEN 1719529 AND 2141947 OR "movie_companies"."movie_id" BETWEEN 2058110 AND 2430451 OR "movie_companies"."movie_id" >= 551600);

SELECT avg("cast_info"."id") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, avg("cast_info"."nr_order") as agg_2 FROM "movie_keyword" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "keyword"."id" <= 91517 AND "title"."episode_nr" >= 66618.19903191681 AND "movie_keyword"."id" BETWEEN 745242 AND 1246610;
SELECT sum("company_type"."id") as agg_0 FROM "company_type"  WHERE "company_type"."kind" IN ('production companies') AND "company_type"."id" = 1;
